    {
      "id": "PopularPost79059",
      "post_content": "If you take the eras they were legal in into consideration, the hordes are better than [helldozer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=helldozer), and much more so.   \n  \nHelldozer did not have [dark ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dark ritual) available, but the hordes did, and thus insured that the opponent would never have more than three lands in play. The hordes also had [instill energy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=instill energy), which let it destroy two lands a turn, or destroy one and attack. If that weren't enough, the only removal spell that could kill the hordes was [swords to plowshares](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=swords to plowshares), but there were many more ways to kill Helldozer by the time Ravnica came around.  \n  \nAlso, the hordes have the flavor, the art and the nostalgia. ",
      "posted_by": "Laguz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost79059\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">If you take the eras they were legal in into consideration, the hordes are better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"helldozer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=helldozer\">helldozer</a>, and much more so. <br/><br/>Helldozer did not have <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"dark ritual\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=dark ritual\">dark ritual</a> available, but the hordes did, and thus insured that the opponent would never have more than three lands in play. The hordes also had <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"instill energy\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=instill energy\">instill energy</a>, which let it destroy two lands a turn, or destroy one and attack. If that weren't enough, the only removal spell that could kill the hordes was <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"swords to plowshares\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=swords to plowshares\">swords to plowshares</a>, but there were many more ways to kill Helldozer by the time Ravnica came around.<br/><br/>Also, the hordes have the flavor, the art and the nostalgia. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '79059'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <