    {
      "id": "PopularPost108799",
      "post_content": "Fireball, Disintegrate, Balance, Wrath of God, Chaos Orb, Chaoslace + Blue Elemental Blast, Thoughtlace + Red Elemental Blast, Drain Life, Earthquake, Meekstone, Nevinyrral's Disk, Northern Paladin, Royal A55a55in, or Pestilence would have dealt with the Hordes in the Beta days, as well. Although few of those are as clean or efficient as StP or modern removal. ",
