      "id": "PopularPost2758",
      "post_content": "What I like most about them compared to [Helldozer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Helldozer):  \n  \n**Blue or white player (bowp):** I steal your Demonic Hordes, hah!  \n**You**: ...  \n*bowps upkeep*  \n**Demonic Hordes:** Give me my black mana.  \n**bowp:** What? Oh, I don't have any.  \n**Demonic Hordes:** I told you give me my black mana until your next upkeep. WHERE IS MY MANA!  \n**bowp:** Calm down man!  \n**Demonic Hordes:** No mana? See that land of yours, I wonder what happens if...  \n**bowp:** Don't do it!  \n**Demonic Hordes:** Whoops, I destroyed it. NOW GIVE ME MY BLACK MANA OR YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS NEXT UPKEEP!  \n  ",
